  "data": {
    "parse": {
      "title": "Cow",
      "pageid": 1904,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\">\n<table id=\"infoboxtable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxheader\">Cow\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 5px;\"><img alt=\"White Cow.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/36/White_Cow.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"90\" height=\"69\" />&#160;<img alt=\"Brown Cow.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3e/Brown_Cow.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"90\" height=\"69\" />\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxdetail\" style=\"text-align: center; font-style: italic;\">Adults can be milked daily. A milk pail is required to harvest the milk.  Lives in the barn.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Building\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Barn.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f8/Barn.png/24px-Barn.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f8/Barn.png/36px-Barn.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/f/f8/Barn.png/48px-Barn.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Purchase Price\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1500 \"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,500g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\">Produce\n</td>\n<td id=\"infoboxdetail\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/24px-Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/36px-Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/24px-Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/36px-Large_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <b>Cow</b> is an <a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">animal</a> that lives in a <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>. Cows can be purchased at <a href=\"/Marnie%27s_Ranch\" title=\"Marnie&#39;s Ranch\">Marnie's Ranch</a> for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1500\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,500g</span>. Cows come in two varieties: White and Brown. When purchasing a cow, the game decides randomly whether you will get a white or brown cow (50% chance). Cows can become pregnant and give <a href=\"/Animals#Animal_Births\" title=\"Animals\">birth</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Produce\">Produce</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Cow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Produce\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>Main article: <a href=\"/Animals#Produce\" title=\"Animals\">Animals#Produce</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Cows who eat every day mature after 5 nights have passed. A mature and fed cow produce <a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> every day. Milk does not vary depending on the color of the Cow, unlike <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Eggs</a>. Once sufficient <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">friendship</a> and happiness is reached, they will produce <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>. Milk can be collected using a <a href=\"/Milk_Pail\" title=\"Milk Pail\">Milk Pail</a>. Milking a cow by hand increases friendship by 5 points. Alternatively, an <a href=\"/Auto-Grabber\" title=\"Auto-Grabber\">Auto-Grabber</a> will automatically milk every cow in a Barn.\n</p><p>Milk can be placed in a <a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a> to produce <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a>, which sells for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"230\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />230g</span> or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"345\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />345g</span> depending on quality.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable roundedborder\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Image\n</th>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<th>Description\n</th>\n<th>Sell Price\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Milk.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a>\n</td>\n<td>A jug of cow's milk.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r146727\">.mw-parser-output .parent,.mw-parser-output .backimage,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent{position:relative;top:0;left:0}.mw-parser-output .backimage img,.mw-parser-output .foreimage img,.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{display:block}.mw-parser-output .backimagetransparent img{opacity:0.6}.mw-parser-output .foreimage{position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0}</style><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/24px-Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/36px-Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>125g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/24px-Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/36px-Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>156g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/24px-Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/36px-Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>187g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/24px-Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/92/Milk.png/36px-Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/92/Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>250g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/File:Large_Milk.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>\n</td>\n<td>A large jug of cow's milk.\n</td>\n<td><table class=\"no-wrap\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-spacing: 0; border: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/24px-Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/36px-Large_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"></div></div></td>\n\t<td>190g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/24px-Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/36px-Large_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Silver Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Silver_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/8/8a/Silver_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>237g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/24px-Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/36px-Large_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Gold Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Gold_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/4/47/Gold_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>285g\n\t</td>\n</tr><tr>\n\t<td><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r146727\"/><div class=\"parent\" style=\"width: 24px; height: auto; margin: 0 auto;\"><div class=\"backimage\"><img alt=\"Large Milk.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/24px-Large_Milk.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/6/67/Large_Milk.png/36px-Large_Milk.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/6/67/Large_Milk.png 2x\" /></div><div class=\"foreimage\"><img alt=\"Iridium Quality Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/24px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png/36px-Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/e/e4/Iridium_Quality_Icon.png 2x\" /></div></div></td>\n\t<td>380g\n\t</td>\n</tr></tbody></table>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Reproduction\">Reproduction</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Cow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Reproduction\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Cows, like <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">pigs</a>, <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">sheep</a>, and <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">goats</a>, have a low chance to reproduce and can produce baby cows. The more animals there are inside the same <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">barn</a>, the higher the chance an animal will give birth.\nWhen it occurs, the player will receive a notice at the bottom of the screen before the day starts, stating \"During the night, [parent's name] gave birth to a baby cow.\" Other than this, there is no indication that a cow is pregnant.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selling\">Selling</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Cow&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Selling\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Cows can be sold. The <a href=\"/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">selling price</a> is dependent on how many <a href=\"/Animals#Friendship\" title=\"Animals\">hearts</a> the animal has (<span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"1950\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />1,950g</span> max).\n</p><p>To sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Animals\" title=\"Animals\">Animals</a> and Produce\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Chicken\" title=\"Chicken\">Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Egg\" title=\"Egg\">Brown Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Egg\" title=\"Large Egg\">Large Brown Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Dinosaur\" title=\"Dinosaur\">Dinosaur</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Dinosaur_Egg\" title=\"Dinosaur Egg\">Dinosaur Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Duck\" title=\"Duck\">Duck</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Duck_Egg\" title=\"Duck Egg\">Duck Egg</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Feather\" title=\"Duck Feather\">Duck Feather</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Golden_Chicken\" title=\"Golden Chicken\">Golden Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Golden_Egg\" title=\"Golden Egg\">Golden Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Rabbit\" title=\"Rabbit\">Rabbit</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a> • <a href=\"/Rabbit%27s_Foot\" title=\"Rabbit&#39;s Foot\">Rabbit's Foot</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Void_Chicken\" title=\"Void Chicken\">Void Chicken</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Void_Egg\" title=\"Void Egg\">Void Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a>\n</th>\n<td><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Cow</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Milk\" title=\"Milk\">Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Milk\" title=\"Large Milk\">Large Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Goat\" title=\"Goat\">Goat</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Goat_Milk\" title=\"Goat Milk\">Goat Milk</a> • <a href=\"/Large_Goat_Milk\" title=\"Large Goat Milk\">Large Goat Milk</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Sheep\" title=\"Sheep\">Sheep</a>  <sup>(<a href=\"/Wool\" title=\"Wool\">Wool</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Ostrich\" title=\"Ostrich\">Ostrich</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Ostrich_Egg\" title=\"Ostrich Egg\">Ostrich Egg</a>)</sup> • <a href=\"/Pig\" title=\"Pig\">Pig</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Truffle\" title=\"Truffle\">Truffle</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Fish\" title=\"Fish\">Fish</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Roe\" title=\"Roe\">Roe</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Slimes\" title=\"Slimes\">Slimes</a> <sup>(<a href=\"/Slime\" title=\"Slime\">Slime</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Ball\" title=\"Slime Ball\">Slime Ball</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Egg\" title=\"Slime Egg\">Slime Egg</a>)</sup>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Other\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Cat</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Cat_or_Dog\" title=\"Animals\">Dog</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Horse\" title=\"Animals\">Horse</a> • <a href=\"/Animals#Additional_Pets\" title=\"Animals\">Turtle</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413180841\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.107 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.122 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3262/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 15891/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1302/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4904/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.006/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 740 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   86.527      1 -total\n 48.50%   41.963      1 Template:Infobox_animal\n 38.49%   33.303      2 Template:Qualityprice\n 30.03%   25.982      3 Template:Description\n 16.44%   14.228      3 Template:Name\n 11.91%   10.304      8 Template:Overlayimg\n  3.44%    2.976      5 Template:Price\n  3.16%    2.736      1 Template:InfoboxSEO\n  1.78%    1.544      1 Template:Main_article\n  1.53%    1.327      1 Template:NavboxAnimals\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1904-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413180841 and revision id 182254\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox animal\n|image    = White Cow.png\n|image2   = Brown Cow.png\n|buyprice = 1500\n|building = {{Name|Barn}}\n|produce  = {{Name|Milk}}{{Name|Large Milk}}\n}}\nThe '''Cow''' is an [[Animals|animal]] that lives in a [[Barn]]. Cows can be purchased at [[Marnie's Ranch]] for {{Price|1500}}. Cows come in two varieties: White and Brown. When purchasing a cow, the game decides randomly whether you will get a white or brown cow (50% chance). Cows can become pregnant and give [[Animals#Animal Births|birth]].\n\n==Produce==\n{{main article|Animals#Produce}}\nCows who eat every day mature after 5 nights have passed. A mature and fed cow produce [[Milk]] every day. Milk does not vary depending on the color of the Cow, unlike [[Egg|Eggs]]. Once sufficient [[Animals#Friendship|friendship]] and happiness is reached, they will produce [[Large Milk]]. Milk can be collected using a [[Milk Pail]]. Milking a cow by hand increases friendship by 5 points. Alternatively, an [[Auto-Grabber]] will automatically milk every cow in a Barn.\n\nMilk can be placed in a [[Cheese Press]] to produce [[Cheese]], which sells for {{Price|230}} or {{Price|345}} depending on quality.\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Image\n!Name\n!Description\n!Sell Price\n|-\n|[[File:Milk.png]]\n|[[Milk]]\n|{{Description|Milk}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Milk|125|dsv=false}}\n|-\n|[[File:Large Milk.png]]\n|[[Large Milk]]\n|{{Description|Large Milk}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Large Milk|190|dsv=false}}\n|}\n\n==Reproduction==\nCows, like [[pig]]s, [[sheep]], and [[goat]]s, have a low chance to reproduce and can produce baby cows. The more animals there are inside the same [[barn]], the higher the chance an animal will give birth.\nWhen it occurs, the player will receive a notice at the bottom of the screen before the day starts, stating \"During the night, [parent's name] gave birth to a baby cow.\" Other than this, there is no indication that a cow is pregnant.\n\n==Selling==\nCows can be sold. The [[gold|selling price]] is dependent on how many [[Animals#Friendship|hearts]] the animal has ({{Price|1950}} max).\n\nTo sell a coop or barn animal, right-click the animal after petting. The friendship/mood interface appears. Move the cursor over the gold coin button at the right to see how much you can sell the animal for. Click that button and the confirmation that follows to complete the sale.\n\n{{NavboxAnimals}}\n\n[[Category:Barn animals]]\n\n[[de:Kuh]]\n[[es:Vaca]]\n[[fr:Vache]]\n[[it:Mucca]]\n[[ja:ウシ]]\n[[ko:소]]\n[[hu:Tehén]]\n[[pt:Vaca]]\n[[ru:Корова]]\n[[tr:İnek]]\n[[zh:牛]]"
